<font color="#FFFFFF">How do you know that?</font>

645
00:59:52,280 --> 00:59:54,290
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shit. That's true. It fits.</font>

646
00:59:55,000 --> 00:59:56,950
<font color="#FFFFFF">So he's a dealer.</font>

647
00:59:57,620 --> 00:59:59,540
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hang on a sec.</font>

648
01:00:09,680 --> 01:00:11,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now we're getting somewhere.</font>

649
01:00:11,760 --> 01:00:13,350
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Discount Inn."</font>

650
01:01:07,320 --> 01:01:09,530
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah, okay. Blonde's fine.</font>

651
01:01:11,910 --> 01:01:14,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's what they say.</font>

652
01:01:14,120 --> 01:01:16,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Discount Inn. 304.</font>

653
01:01:17,240 --> 01:01:18,290
