666
01:02:16,300 --> 01:02:18,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">Whatever gets you off.</font>

667
01:02:42,700 --> 01:02:44,830
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't blame the cops
for not taking me seriously.</font>

668
01:02:44,910 --> 01:02:47,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is a difficult condition
