680
01:03:16,780 --> 01:03:19,410
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mrs. Jankis, the company's position
isn't that Sammy is faking anything...</font>

681
01:03:19,490 --> 01:03:21,410
<font color="#FFFFFF">just that his condition
can't be shown to be...</font>

682
01:03:21,490 --> 01:03:24,950
<font color="#FFFFFF">I just want to know what your honest
opinion about Sammy is.</font>

683
01:03:25,040 --> 01:03:27,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">We shouldn't even be talking like this
while the case is still open to appeal.</font>

684
01:03:28,040 --> 01:03:31,290
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'm not appealing the decision.
