686
01:03:33,920 --> 01:03:37,380
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't see some... vegetable.</font>

687
01:03:37,470 --> 01:03:39,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">I see my same old Sammy.</font>

688
01:03:41,720 --> 01:03:44,526
<font color="#FFFFFF">What do you think that's like for me
