697
01:04:14,750 --> 01:04:18,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">and tell me if you really believe
that Sammy's faking his condition.</font>

698
01:04:19,590 --> 01:04:23,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need to know... what you
honestly believe.</font>

699
01:04:29,020 --> 01:04:32,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">I believe that Sammy should be physically
capable of making new memories.</font>

700
01:04:40,530 --> 01:04:41,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

701
01:04:44,280 --> 01:04:47,200
<font color="#FFFFFF">I thought I helped her. I thought
she just needed some kind of answer.</font>

702
01:04:47,290 --> 01:04:49,290
<font color="#FFFFFF">I didn't think it was important
what the answer was...</font>

703
01:04:50,120 --> 01:04:52,120
<font color="#FFFFFF">just that she had
one to believe.</font>

704
01:05:07,220 --> 01:05:10,060
<font color="#FFFFFF">- A car this nice you should lock.
