01:06:16,710 --> 01:06:18,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is the bar where she works.</font>

728
01:06:18,750 --> 01:06:20,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">Her boyfriend's a drug dealer.</font>

729
01:06:20,880 --> 01:06:23,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">She takes orders
for him, arranges meets.</font>

730
01:06:23,590 --> 01:06:26,470
