01:06:35,600 --> 01:06:36,810
<font color="#FFFFFF">From who?</font>

735
01:06:36,900 --> 01:06:39,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">Guys are gonna wanna know
what happened to her boyfriend.</font>

736
01:06:39,730 --> 01:06:43,280
<font color="#FFFFFF">Guys are gonna come after her.
