738
01:06:46,490 --> 01:06:49,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, yeah? Maybe she'll make it you.
Is that it?</font>

739
01:06:50,080 --> 01:06:51,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">You worried that she's gonna
use me against you?</font>

740
01:06:52,080 --> 01:06:54,080
<font color="#FFFFFF">- No.
- Why not?</font>

741
01:06:54,790 --> 01:06:57,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because she doesn't
know who I am.</font>

742
01:06:58,420 --> 01:07:00,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Why are you following me?
