744
01:07:05,050 --> 01:07:07,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">So write this down.</font>

745
01:07:07,800 --> 01:07:12,470
<font color="#FFFFFF">When she offers to help,
it'll be for her own reasons.</font>

746
01:07:12,560 --> 01:07:17,350
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not lying. Take my pen.
