749
01:07:30,620 --> 01:07:32,530
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why not?</font>

750
01:07:32,620 --> 01:07:34,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">You ever wonder how long
you can hang around here</font>

751
01:07:34,434 --> 01:07:36,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">before people start
asking questions?</font>

752
01:07:36,610 --> 01:07:37,290
<font color="#FFFFFF">What sort of questions?</font>

753
01:07:37,370 --> 01:07:39,500
<font color="#FFFFFF">The same sort of questions you
should be asking yourself.</font>

754
01:07:39,580 --> 01:07:42,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Like what?
- Like, how did you get this suit, the car?</font>

755
01:07:42,210 --> 01:07:43,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I have money.
- From what?</font>

756
01:07:43,920 --> 01:07:47,300
