on it in the dead man's hand.</font>

947
01:20:27,430 --> 01:20:29,390
<font color="#FFFFFF">And they only found my gun.</font>

948
01:20:29,980 --> 01:20:32,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">They didn't need to look
for anybody else.</font>

949
01:20:33,770 --> 01:20:36,780
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was the only guy who disagreed
with the facts, and I had brain damage.</font>

950
01:20:37,570 --> 01:20:39,490
<font color="#FFFFFF">The cops are not gonna believe
someone in my condition.</font>

951
01:20:39,570 --> 01:20:43,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">Leonard, you can stay here for a couple
of days if it'll help you.</font>

952
01:20:46,080 --> 01:20:47,250
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thanks.</font>

953
01:20:47,330 --> 01:20:49,790
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have to go back to work.</font>

954
01:20:49,870 --> 01:20:52,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">So, just make yourself at home.</font>

955
01:20:52,210 --> 01:20:56,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">You can watch TV or you can have
some food, whatever you want, okay?</font>

956
01:20:56,130 --> 01:20:58,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Make yourself at home.
- One thing.</font>

957
01:21:01,890 --> 01:21:05,640
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Something to remember you by.
- My name is Natalie.</font>

958
01:21:08,100 --> 01:21:10,020
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Natalie."</font>

959
01:21:42,260 --> 01:21:44,390
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What's wrong?
- Somebody's come already.</font>

960
01:22:33,690 --> 01:22:35,690
<font color="#FFFFFF">- On the house.
- Thanks.</font>

961
01:22:41,190 --> 01:22:43,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">You really do have a problem.</font>

962
01:22:43,860 --> 01:22:45,700
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just like that cop said.</font>

963
01:22:47,200 --> 01:22:48,450
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your condition.</font>

964
01:22:49,540 --> 01:22:51,040
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nobody's perfect.</font>

965
01:22:52,620 --> 01:22:56,040
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's the last thing
that you do remember?</font>

966
01:22:59,170 --> 01:23:01,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">- My wife.
- That's sweet.</font>

967
01:23:01,380 --> 01:23:02,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dying.</font>

968
01:23:03,670 --> 01:23:05,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">I remember my wife dying.</font>

969
01:23:10,260 --> 01:23:12,310
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me get you another one.</font>

970
01:23:13,270 --> 01:23:15,230
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think this one's dusty.</font>

971
01:23:19,690 --> 01:23:21,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why are you calling me?
What do you want?</font>

972
01:23:22,480 --> 01:23:25,280
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know you're a cop, but what do you want?
Have I done something wrong?</font>

973
01:23:26,200 --> 01:23:28,320
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't know.
Something bad, maybe.</font>

974
01:23:30,910 --> 01:23:32,674
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why are you asking me? I can't
remember what I've done.</font>

975
01:23:32,699 --> 01:23:34,814
<font color="#FFFFFF">You wouldn't believe me anyway.</font>

976
01:23:34,870 --> 01:23:37,790
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because of my condition. You don't
believe someone with this condition.</font>

977
01:23:37,880 --> 01:23:40,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nobody believed Sammy! I didn't
even fucking believe Sammy!</font>

978
01:23:41,420 --> 01:23:43,170
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Ferdy's Bar."</font>

979
01:23:45,470 --> 01:23:48,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Come by after. Natalie."</font>

980
01:24:02,320 --> 01:24:04,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll have a beer, please.</font>

981
01:24:04,110 --> 01:24:06,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What do you want?
- A beer, please.</font>

982
01:24:06,190 --> 01:24:08,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">You can't just waltz in here dressed
like that and ask for a beer.</font>

983
01:24:08,700 --> 01:24:11,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What, is there a dress code?
- Why are you here?</font>

984
01:24:11,120 --> 01:24:14,080
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'm meeting someone called Natalie.
