985
01:24:14,160 --> 01:24:16,370
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. We met before, right?</font>

986
01:24:17,750 --> 01:24:20,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Then why am I here?
- I don't know. Why don't you tell me.</font>

987
01:24:20,080 --> 01:24:22,540
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't remember. I have no
short-term memory. It's not amnesia.</font>

988
01:24:22,630 --> 01:24:25,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You're the memory guy.
- How do you know about me?</font>

989
01:24:26,130 --> 01:24:27,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">My boyfriend told me about you.</font>

990
01:24:27,930 --> 01:24:31,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Yeah? Who's your boyfriend?
- Jimmy Grants. Do you know him?</font>

991
01:24:33,010 --> 01:24:34,470
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

992
01:24:34,560 --> 01:24:38,020
<font color="#FFFFFF">He knows you. He
told me about you.</font>

993
01:24:38,100 --> 01:24:40,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">He said you were staying
at the Discount.</font>

994
01:24:40,270 --> 01:24:43,310
<font color="#FFFFFF">In fact, a cop came by earlier,
