995
01:24:43,400 --> 01:24:45,570
<font color="#FFFFFF">Said he was looking for a guy
who can't remember anything...</font>

996
01:24:45,650 --> 01:24:47,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">wouldn't know how he got
here or what he'd done.</font>

997
01:24:48,070 --> 01:24:50,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">Said I get a lot of guys
around here like that.</font>

998
01:24:50,700 --> 01:24:54,160
<font color="#FFFFFF">Chronic alcoholism is one cause
of short-term memory loss.</font>

999
01:24:56,240 --> 01:24:58,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Are you Teddy?
- No. My name's Leonard.</font>

1000
01:24:59,040 --> 01:25:01,170
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Did Teddy send you?
- I don't know.</font>

1001
01:25:02,750 --> 01:25:05,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What's happened to Jimmy?
- I don't know that either.</font>

1002
01:25:05,500 --> 01:25:07,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Sorry.
- You don't remember anything?</font>

1003
01:25:07,970 --> 01:25:11,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't remember where
you've been or what you've just done.</font>

1004
01:25:11,390 --> 01:25:15,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">No. I can't make new memories.
Everything just fades.</font>

1005
01:25:15,100 --> 01:25:17,810
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Then why did you come here?
- I found this in my pocket.</font>

1006
01:25:21,100 --> 01:25:22,600
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Your</i> pocket.</font>

1007
01:25:47,250 --> 01:25:50,380
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bar bet. Care to contribute?</font>

1008
01:25:50,470 --> 01:25:52,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">- No, thanks.
- It's for a lot of money.</font>

1009
01:25:53,390 --> 01:25:56,350
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on. Proceeds are going to charity.
Help me out.</font>

1010
01:26:08,610 --> 01:26:09,900
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

1011
01:26:27,340 --> 01:26:29,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">- On the house.
- Thanks.</font>

1012
01:26:34,220 --> 01:26:36,590
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's completely fucked
because nobody believes you.</font>

1013
01:26:37,800 --> 01:26:41,060
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's amazing what a little brain
damage will do for your credibility.</font>

1014
01:26:41,140 --> 01:26:43,930
<font color="#FFFFFF">I guess it's some kind of poetic
justice for not believing Sammy.</font>

1015
01:26:44,020 --> 01:26:46,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know the truth
about my condition, Officer?</font>

1016
01:26:47,020 --> 01:26:49,020
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't know anything.</font>

1017
01:26:49,110 --> 01:26:51,280
<font color="#FFFFFF">You feel angry, you
don't know why.</font>

1018
01:26:51,360 --> 01:26:54,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">You feel guilty, you
have no idea why.</font>

1019
01:26:54,950 --> 01:26:57,570
<font color="#FFFFFF">You could do anything and not have
the faintest idea 10 minutes later.</font>

1020
01:26:57,660 --> 01:27:00,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like Sammy. What if I've done
something like Sammy?</font>

1021
01:27:00,740 --> 01:27:04,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">I didn't tell you what happened
to Sammy and his wife?</font>

1022
01:27:05,750 --> 01:27:08,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">She came to see me at my office. I thought
she was trying to catch me off guard...</font>

1023
01:27:09,000 --> 01:27:11,920
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>so I didn't tell her what I really thought,
