1024
01:27:12,010 --> 01:27:13,920
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>just that his condition
was mental, not physical.</i></font>

1025
01:27:14,010 --> 01:27:16,970
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I found out later that she went
home and gave Sammy his final exam.</i></font>

1026
01:27:18,680 --> 01:27:21,640
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sammy? It's time for my shot.</font>

1027
01:27:37,610 --> 01:27:39,620
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>She knew beyond a doubt
that he loved her.</i></font>

1028
01:27:40,780 --> 01:27:42,740
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>So she found a way to test him.</i></font>

1029
01:27:55,470 --> 01:27:59,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sammy. It's time for my shot.</font>

1030
01:28:09,020 --> 01:28:11,060
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>She really thought
she'd call his bluff.</i></font>

1031
01:28:11,150 --> 01:28:12,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">There you go.</font>

1032
01:28:13,230 --> 01:28:17,070
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Or she just didn't wanna live
with the things she'd put him through.</i></font>

1033
01:28:27,040 --> 01:28:28,040
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sammy.</font>

