1038
01:29:32,310 --> 01:29:34,230
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's been in a home ever since.</font>

1039
01:29:34,310 --> 01:29:36,730
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>He doesn't even know
that his wife is dead.</i></font>

1040
01:29:36,820 --> 01:29:40,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was wrong about Sammy,
and I was wrong about his wife.</font>

1041
01:29:40,280 --> 01:29:42,200
<font color="#FFFFFF">She wasn't interested
in the money.</font>

1042
01:29:42,280 --> 01:29:44,450
<font color="#FFFFFF">She just needed
to understand his problem.</font>

1043
01:29:44,530 --> 01:29:47,950
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>His brain didn't respond to conditioning.
But he wasn't a con man.</i></font>

1044
01:29:48,040 --> 01:29:51,460
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>When she looked into his eyes,
she thought he could be the same person.</i></font>

1045
01:29:51,540 --> 01:29:53,920
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>When I looked into his eyes,
I thought I saw recognition.</i></font>

1046
01:29:54,000 --> 01:29:56,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now I know. You fake it.</font>

1047
01:29:56,210 --> 01:29:59,050
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you think you're supposed to recognize
somebody, you just pretend to.</font>

1048
01:29:59,130 --> 01:30:01,800
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>You bluff it to get a pat
on the head from the doctors.</i></font>

1049
01:30:02,430 --> 01:30:04,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">You bluff it to seem
less of a freak.</font>

1050
01:30:08,310 --> 01:30:10,020
<font color="#FFFFFF">What drug dealer?</font>

1051
01:30:35,420 --> 01:30:38,540
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hey, Lenny, how you doing?
- It's private back here.</font>

1052
01:30:38,630 --> 01:30:41,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">- It's okay. We know each other. Right, kid?
- How did you know I was in here?</font>

1053
01:30:41,720 --> 01:30:43,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Jag's out front. Should
have put it around back.</font>

1054
01:30:43,800 --> 01:30:47,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you still doing here, Lenny?
There's plenty of tattoo parlors up north.</font>

1055
01:30:47,390 --> 01:30:49,890
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, I guess I wanted to get something
down before it slipped my mind.</font>

1056
01:30:49,970 --> 01:30:51,484
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right then, give me the keys.
I'll move it for you.</font>

1057
01:30:51,509 --> 01:30:52,454
<font color="#FFFFFF">It'll be all right
for a minute.</font>

1058
01:30:52,520 --> 01:30:54,020
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait out there.</font>

1059
01:30:54,850 --> 01:30:57,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">Give me a minute. I gotta
get something for you.</font>

1060
01:31:01,190 --> 01:31:05,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fact six: Car license SG 137IU.</font>

1061
01:31:11,290 --> 01:31:13,540
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look. Wait a minute, will ya?</font>

1062
01:31:17,040 --> 01:31:19,080
<font color="#FFFFFF">- We gotta get you out of here.
- Why?</font>

1063
01:31:19,170 --> 01:31:22,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">Man. Come on, Leonard. How
many times I gotta tell you?</font>

1064
01:31:22,550 --> 01:31:24,328
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's not safe for you
to hang around here anymore.</font>

1065
01:31:24,353 --> 01:31:24,945
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why not?</font>

1066
01:31:25,010 --> 01:31:26,930
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because that cop's looking
for you.</font>

1067
01:31:27,010 --> 01:31:29,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">I gotta get you a new
identity, some new clothes.</font>

1068
01:31:29,680 --> 01:31:32,310
<font color="#FFFFFF">A different car would do for now.
So put these on.</font>

1069
01:31:32,390 --> 01:31:33,770
<font color="#FFFFFF">What cop?</font>

1070
01:31:34,980 --> 01:31:37,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's a bad cop. He's the one that checked
you into the Discount Inn.</font>

1071
01:31:38,020 --> 01:31:39,976
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's been calling you for days
now, telling you shit,</font>

1072
01:31:40,001 --> 01:31:41,884
<font color="#FFFFFF">slipping envelopes under your door.
Shit like that.</font>

1073
01:31:41,940 --> 01:31:44,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">- How do you know this?
- He told me. He thinks it's funny.</font>

1074
01:31:44,740 --> 01:31:46,740
<font color="#FFFFFF">- He's been laughing at you.
- You're full of shit.</font>

1075
01:31:46,820 --> 01:31:49,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not. He knows you're no good
on the phone, so he's been calling you.</font>

1076
01:31:49,740 --> 01:31:51,740
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sometimes you don't
answer the phone...</font>

1077
01:31:51,830 --> 01:31:54,620
<font color="#FFFFFF">so he slips shit under your door to scare
you into answering the phone again...</font>

1078
01:31:54,700 --> 01:31:57,370
<font color="#FFFFFF">giving you a line of crap about John G.
being some local drug dealer.</font>

1079
01:31:57,460 --> 01:32:00,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Jimmy Grants.
- Who's Jimmy Grants?</font>

1080
01:32:00,790 --> 01:32:02,750
<font color="#FFFFFF">Leonard,
Jimmy's the drug dealer.</font>

1081
01:32:02,840 --> 01:32:05,130
<font color="#FFFFFF">The cop wants to know
how his operation's run.</font>

1082
01:32:05,220 --> 01:32:07,220
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's got some score in mind.
Somehow you're involved.</font>

1083
01:32:07,300 --> 01:32:08,970
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh-huh. How do you know him?</font>

1084
01:32:10,050 --> 01:32:14,770
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm a snitch. He's a cop from out of town.
The local boys put us together.</font>

1085
01:32:14,850 --> 01:32:17,180
<font color="#FFFFFF">If he knew I was helping
you, he'd fucking kill me.</font>

1086
01:32:17,270 --> 01:32:21,060
<font color="#FFFFFF">So take these clothes, put them
on and get the fuck out of here.</font>

1087
01:32:21,150 --> 01:32:23,770
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, Leonard. Just go.</font>

1088
01:32:44,420 --> 01:32:46,380
<font color="#FFFFFF">You are full of shit.</font>

1089
01:32:48,090 --> 01:32:50,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Come by after. Natalie."</font>

1090
01:32:50,340 --> 01:32:51,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Ferdy's Bar."</font>

1091
01:33:34,680 --> 01:33:36,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Jimmy.</font>

1092
01:33:39,060 --> 01:33:41,850
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry. I thought you
were somebody else.</font>

1093
01:33:42,520 --> 01:33:43,850
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sorry.</font>

1094
01:33:44,690 --> 01:33:45,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's okay.</font>

1095
01:34:00,120 --> 01:34:03,370
<font color="#FFFFFF">So this Jimmy Grants deals drugs
out of the bar where his girlfriend works?</font>

1096
01:34:04,210 --> 01:34:06,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">But he's not gonna bring her along.
He'll come by himself, right?</font>

1097
01:34:08,050 --> 01:34:11,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">I always figured the drugs angle
would be the best way to get him.</font>

1098
01:34:12,050 --> 01:34:15,220
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, Officer. I'm as ready
as I'll ever be.</font>

1099
01:34:15,930 --> 01:34:18,470
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're in the lobby?
What do you look like?</font>

1100
01:34:19,770 --> 01:34:21,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll be right there.</font>

1101
01:35:03,850 --> 01:35:04,770
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lenny.</font>

1102
01:35:07,900 --> 01:35:09,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">Officer Gammell.</font>

1103
01:35:11,650 --> 01:35:14,360
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. Come on.</font>

1104
01:35:30,880 --> 01:35:33,340
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Smile.
- Not here.</font>

1105
01:35:34,670 --> 01:35:35,970
<font color="#FFFFFF">Over here.</font>

1106
01:35:41,640 --> 01:35:44,640
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Is it Officer or Lieutenant Gammell?
- You know what?</font>

1107
01:35:44,730 --> 01:35:46,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't write Gammell, just Teddy.</font>

1108
01:35:47,600 --> 01:35:49,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Why?
- I'm undercover.</font>

1109
01:35:52,480 --> 01:35:54,900
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is the directions
where he's going.</font>

1110
01:35:54,990 --> 01:35:58,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">- My number's on the bottom if you need me.
- You're not coming?</font>

1111
01:35:58,110 --> 01:36:00,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">No. It wouldn't be appropriate.</font>

1112
01:36:04,580 --> 01:36:07,660
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nice picture. I look thin.</font>

1113
01:36:11,380 --> 01:36:12,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Lenny.</font>

1114
01:36:13,340 --> 01:36:14,760
<font color="#FFFFFF">Make him beg.</font>

1115
01:37:37,840 --> 01:37:39,090
<font color="#FFFFFF">Teddy!</font>

1116
01:37:42,300 --> 01:37:43,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Teddy!</font>

1117
01:37:50,770 --> 01:37:51,940
<font color="#FFFFFF">Jimmy.</font>

1118
01:37:53,730 --> 01:37:56,310
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What the fuck are you doing here?
- You Jimmy Grants?</font>

1119
01:37:56,400 --> 01:37:58,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">Expecting any other Jimmys
out here, Memory Man?</font>

1120
01:37:58,480 --> 01:38:02,740
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Do you remember me?
- Yeah, I remember you.</font>

1121
01:38:02,820 --> 01:38:05,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where the fuck's Teddy?</font>

1122
01:38:05,320 --> 01:38:06,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well?</font>

1123
01:38:10,160 --> 01:38:12,960
